   SCI-CONTACT-LENSES (Undated) _ Buying contact lenses has never
been easier. Besides the traditional outlets, like optometrists'
offices and mail order stores, they can be found on hundreds of Web
sites and even at beauty salons and local flea markets. But now
authorities are cracking down on those sold without prescriptions.
By Susan Gilbert.
</P>
<P>
   SCI-Q&AMP;A (Undated) _ Science question answered: What is the
difference between dentists with D.D.S. after their names and those
with D.M.D.?
</P>
