<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-21 14:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5343 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u w BC-OLIPHANT-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      12-21 0931
