<HEADER>
A5387 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v AM-ADD-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      12-21 0678
</HEADER>
<BODY>
 AM-ADD-NYT-BUDGET  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Add N.Y. Times News Service budget for papers of WEDNESDAY, Dec.
22.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; DINING &LR;  (``d'' code)
