<P>
   SOC-NOTEBOOK (Undated) _ Eduard Hurtado went from the MetroStars
to the Revolution, teams known for floundering rather than
flourishing. In between he found success in Ecuador, his home
country. By Frank Dell'Apa.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
