   BKN-HAWKS-TERRY _ ATLANTA _ When Jason Terry was acquired with
the 10th pick of the 1999 NBA draft, it was thought that he would
jump immediately into the starting lineup and lead the new-look
Atlanta Hawks. Although he hasn't worked his way into the starting
lineup, Terry is playing a key role off the bench for the team. He
has played well in spots, but has also shown the mistakes of a
rookie. A look at the play of the Hawks' top pick after the first
20 games of the season. (Denberg, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
25.
