</P>
<P>
   FBN-KEARSE _ Former Florida player Jevon Kearse has overcome a
number of obstacles during his trip to the NFL's limelight. Kearse
set the record for rookie sacks last week and is a major reason the
Tennessee Titans are in the playoffs. Tennessee plays Jacksonville
on Sunday in an AFC Central showdown. (Schlabach, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 40.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-FALCONS-REBUILD _ ATLANTA _ For better or worse, the Falcons
face a tremendous rebuilding task during the offseason. The 2000
team will have a lot of new players. (Winkeljohn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 13.
</P>
