<P>
   INTERNET-SCAMS _ WASHINGTON _ The Federal Trade Commission
announced Tuesday it is cracking down on hundreds of companies that
use the Internet to con people with pyramid schemes. These
old-fashioned scams are proliferating in the new cyber-environment.
(Geewax, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 18.
