<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   TERROR-GROUP (Washington) _ The hunger for information on Osama
bin Laden, and two Algerians suspected as terrorist agents, is
growing as the days tick off to the end of the millennium. By John
Donnelly. (i, w and a coding)
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON (w) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MILLENNIUM-THREATS (Washington) _ White House summons top
national security officials for discussions about whether
additional public warnings should be made about a possible
terrorist threat as the millennium approaches, but the meeting was
