<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-21 19:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5674 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i BC-TERROR-GROUP-BOS &LR;      12-21 1131
