of people come to pawn shops,'' said Paula Newhouse, manager of the
Best Collateral pawn shop on Mission Street. ``They know they'll
get good value.'' In fact, visits to a number of downtown pawn
shops revealed that monthly sales rise by about 30 percent every
December as customers seek out bargain-priced jewelry, electronics
goods, musical instruments and other stuff to give as holiday
presents. By David Lazarus
